                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Merry</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">San Salvador</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-07-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 22, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Merry states that he has received a telegram from the President of Honduras
                    requesting him to present to the President of the United States the gratitude of
                    the Government and people of Honduras for his friendly and efficient mediation
                    in obtaining peace tween Guatemala, Salvador, and Honduras.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
